CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B7, reads: "PROFESSIONALS....Albert Simmons of New Kensington, inset. received his Bachelor of Science in Pharmacy Degree..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three men wearing dark caps and gowns, including Albert Simmons in center, after receiving Bachelor of Science in Pharmacy Degree, at University of Pittsburgh graduation
